<plot>A light-hearted look at 30 years of "Page 3" girls, starting with the very first to the household names like Linda Lussardi and Samantha Fox. Taking the story up to the present, young inexperienced models describe their ambitions in a different world, as they do a photo shoot for the newspaper. Journalists, editors and commentators talk of the impact Page 3 has had.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?537170</url></doc>
